<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'About — ' + (profile.name || 'Portfolio') }) %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header', { page }) %>

<!-- HERO SECTION 2 -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">About Me</div>
    <h1>The person behind the <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--violet)">work.</em></h1>
  </div>
  <% if (heroPhotos.length) { %>
  <div class="marquee-wrap">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <% heroPhotos.concat(heroPhotos).forEach(function(h){ %>
        <img src="<%= h.image %>" alt="">
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% } %>
</section>

<!-- BIO -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top:60px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-photo reveal">
        <img src="<%= profile.profile_photo || '/img/placeholder.svg' %>" alt="<%= profile.name %>">
        <div class="frame"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">Bio</div>
        <h2 style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:18px;"><%= profile.name %></h2>
        <div class="about-bio">
          <p><%= profile.bio %></p>
        </div>
        <% if (profile.resume_link) { %>
          <a href="<%= profile.resume_link %>" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:12px;">Download Resume</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container"><div class="divider"></div></div>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Skills</div>
      <h2>Tools of the trade</h2>
      <p>Technologies and tools I use to bring ideas to life.</p>
    </div>
    <% if (skills.length) { %>
    <div class="skills-grid reveal-stagger">
      <% skills.forEach(function(s){ %>
      <div class="skill-card glass">
        <% if (s.image) { %><img src="<%= s.image %>" alt="<%= s.title %>">
        <% } else { %><div class="fallback-icon"><%= s.title.slice(0,2).toUpperCase() %></div><% } %>
        <span><%= s.title %></span>
      </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div class="empty-state"><strong>No skills added yet</strong>Add your skills and their icons from the dashboard.</div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container"><div class="divider"></div></div>

<!-- EDUCATION -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Education</div>
      <h2>Academic background</h2>
    </div>
    <% if (education.length) { %>
    <div class="timeline glass reveal" style="padding:8px 28px;">
      <% education.forEach(function(e){ %>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year"><%= e.year %></div>
        <div>
          <h4><%= e.degree %></h4>
          <div class="org"><%= e.institution %></div>
          <% if (e.description) { %><p><%= e.description %></p><% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div class="empty-state"><strong>No education added yet</strong>Add your academic history from the dashboard.</div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container"><div class="divider"></div></div>

<!-- TRAININGS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Trainings &amp; Certifications</div>
      <h2>Always leveling up</h2>
    </div>
    <% if (trainings.length) { %>
    <div class="timeline glass reveal" style="padding:8px 28px;">
      <% trainings.forEach(function(t){ %>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year"><%= t.year %></div>
        <div>
          <h4><%= t.title %></h4>
          <div class="org"><%= t.organization %></div>
          <% if (t.description) { %><p><%= t.description %></p><% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div class="empty-state"><strong>No trainings added yet</strong>Add certifications and trainings from the dashboard.</div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container"><div class="divider"></div></div>

<!-- HOBBIES -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Beyond work</div>
      <h2>Hobbies &amp; interests</h2>
    </div>
    <% if (hobbies.length) { %>
    <div class="hobbies-row reveal-stagger">
      <% hobbies.forEach(function(h){ %>
      <div class="hobby-chip glass"><%= h.icon || '✦' %> <%= h.title %></div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div class="empty-state"><strong>No hobbies added yet</strong>Add a few from the dashboard to show your personality.</div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer', { profile }) %>
</body>
</html>
